text: Gureyev or Gureev () is a Russian-language surname. The feminine form of this name is Gureyeva or Gureeva (). Notable people who share this surname include: *Lyudmila Gureyeva (1943–2017), Soviet volleyball player *Zhanna Gureyeva (born 1970), Belarusian triple jumper Category:Russian-language surnames
